MrPokemonHouse_Text_Intro3:
	.string "I know a couple who run a\n"
	.string "POKéMON DAY-CARE service.\p"
	.string "They gave me that EGG.\p"
	.string "I was intrigued, so I sent\n"
	.string "mail to PROF.ELM.\p"
